  <entry>
    <title>gitee</title>
    <link href="/2022/05/31/gitee/"/>
    <url>/2022/05/31/gitee/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Git-全局设置"><a href="#Git-全局设置" class="headerlink" title="Git 全局设置:"></a>Git 全局设置:</h2><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">git config <span class="hljs-attr">--global</span> user<span class="hljs-selector-class">.name</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;ChangerC77&quot;</span><br>git config <span class="hljs-attr">--global</span> user<span class="hljs-selector-class">.email</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;1216898523@qq.com&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="创建-git-仓库"><a href="#创建-git-仓库" class="headerlink" title="创建 git 仓库:"></a>创建 git 仓库:</h2><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs vim"><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> gitee<br><span class="hljs-keyword">cd</span> gitee<br>git init <br>touch README.md<br>git <span class="hljs-built_in">add</span> README.md<br>git commit -<span class="hljs-keyword">m</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;first commit&quot;</span><br>git remote <span class="hljs-built_in">add</span> origin https://gitee.<span class="hljs-keyword">com</span>/arx-discover/gitee.git<br>git push -<span class="hljs-keyword">u</span> origin <span class="hljs-string">&quot;master&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="已有仓库"><a href="#已有仓库" class="headerlink" title="已有仓库?"></a>已有仓库?</h2><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">cd existing_git_repo<br>git remote add origin https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//gi</span>tee.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/arx-discover/gi</span>tee.git<br>git push -u origin <span class="hljs-string">&quot;master&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>0代码0成本搭建个人博客</title>
    <link href="/2022/05/29/0%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%810%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <url>/2022/05/29/0%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%810%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一、配置Git"><a href="#一、配置Git" class="headerlink" title="一、配置Git"></a>一、配置Git</h1><p>1、设置用户名、邮箱</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">$ git config <span class="hljs-attr">--global</span> user<span class="hljs-selector-class">.name</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;username&quot;</span><br>$ git config <span class="hljs-attr">--global</span> user<span class="hljs-selector-class">.email</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;*****@163.com&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2 、创建新的ssh keys</p><figure class="highlight elixir"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs elixir"><span class="hljs-variable">$ </span>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="hljs-string">&quot;*****@163.com&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="生成两个文件："><a href="#生成两个文件：" class="headerlink" title="生成两个文件："></a>生成两个文件：</h3><ul><li>id_rsa：私钥（只能个人看）</li><li>id_rsa.pub：公钥（可以发布出去的）</li></ul><blockquote><p>*****@163.com为开发者标识，不一定必须为邮箱号<br>若为Windows系统，公钥一般会存储在</p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">C:\Users\(用户名）<span class="hljs-regexp">/.ssh/i</span>d_rsa<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3、将公钥填写到github中的Setting&gt;SSH and GPG keys<br>● 公钥默认地址位于~/ssh/id_rsa.pub<br>Windows电脑上无法打开id_rsa.pub文件，复制一个副本，把后缀改为txt即可查看</p></blockquote><h1 id="二、登录Github"><a href="#二、登录Github" class="headerlink" title="二、登录Github"></a>二、登录Github</h1><h2 id="1-进入Settings"><a href="#1-进入Settings" class="headerlink" title="1. 进入Settings"></a>1. 进入Settings</h2><ul><li>进入SSH and GPG keys<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/a74b140d406747c7b727be1db06c9bc5.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></li><li>创建一个新的SSH<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/fdff44004d08436e873949e4b505e94e.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"><br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/fade279cb4eb4dd8bdf57ab8d1ce4cc0.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></li></ul><h2 id="2-创建新的仓库"><a href="#2-创建新的仓库" class="headerlink" title="2. 创建新的仓库"></a>2. 创建新的仓库</h2><p> <img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/83dddc4d6cd14565878d97b1b4e6bf00.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></p><blockquote><p>仓库名要和Owner一致</p></blockquote><h1 id="二、安装Hexo"><a href="#二、安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="二、安装Hexo"></a>二、安装Hexo</h1><ul><li>安装</li></ul><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs avrasm">npm install hexo-<span class="hljs-keyword">cli</span> g<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="三、环境搭建"><a href="#三、环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="三、环境搭建"></a>三、环境搭建</h1><ul><li>新建一个project<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/15a68e54d1c149bb8f4d6a1f47e71854.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></li><li>初始化</li></ul><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs csharp">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">init</span> <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>提示文件夹非空<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/0ab7b92542154228999262d76026419f.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"><br>解决方案：<br>打开工程所在目录，显示隐藏文件，删掉隐藏文件<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/5da2696671a347f1b6663dd7f968bbf5.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"><br>删掉.idea</p><ul><li>再次初始化</li></ul><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs csharp">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">init</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/92539fe08acf48a1bbeb14972da35669.png" alt="请添加图片描述"></p><ul><li>文件结构<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/67e6a3869fae4411a73b1b568bd0ba95.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></li><li>_config.yaml文件<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/c966f65a1978406b988ae5f30d1ea1ac.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></li><li>修改成自己的<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/1430a359c1c843a9ba3bb4ff0449e498.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></li><li>构建网页</li></ul><figure class="highlight axapta"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs axapta">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">server</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/77933f5eeabf4a68b52f3d2a2393632f.png" alt="请添加图片描述"><br>显示页面<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/36da2cbefca140efaaf6cfe2f42d1e8b.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></p><h1 id="1-推荐主题"><a href="#1-推荐主题" class="headerlink" title="1. 推荐主题"></a>1. 推荐主题<img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/cc5adfb8ceca4f25921502175d463c1d.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></h1><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2d51fb687fb84320b0f069c82b99f621.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"><br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/92fe223188d048cca1ef00fa7cb1eeb3.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></p><ul><li>下载解压使用主题<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/35524da09c8045f7bf12c7bed2f475fa.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></li><li>适配主题<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/35140f5d6fe24e7ab801fd7a24f1b127.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></li><li>修改主题名<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/fe8fdc64c40c42fa98ef92b6675a63f3.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></li><li>清除缓存</li></ul><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo clean</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>再次构建网页</li></ul><figure class="highlight axapta"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs axapta">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">server</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>如果之前已有博客网页，刷新网页即可</p></blockquote><h1 id="四、编写我的博文"><a href="#四、编写我的博文" class="headerlink" title="四、编写我的博文"></a>四、编写我的博文</h1><h3 id="重要博客结构"><a href="#重要博客结构" class="headerlink" title="重要博客结构"></a>重要博客结构</h3><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/8e4e83f06f13406fa18bfe6351469d64.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ2hhbmdlckM=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></p><ul><li>souce</li><li>themes</li><li>_config.yaml</li></ul><h2 id="新建博客"><a href="#新建博客" class="headerlink" title="新建博客"></a>新建博客</h2><figure class="highlight haxe"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs haxe">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-type">post</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;我的第一篇博客&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>构建网页</li></ul><figure class="highlight axapta"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs axapta">hexo clean<br>hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">server</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>生成网页文件<figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo g</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>推送到github<figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo d</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
